name: U.F.I.S.H.
description:
It was just another fishing day went somebody shot our ship and we lost our anti-gravity engine. You must find the engines down the water and deep inside the darkest places of the ocean. Don't forget to use your tracking beam to fish some dinner and also to catch some coins that you could shoot to defend yourself!!
Controls:

  •  ARROWS/WASD to move.
  • SPACE: activate tracking beam
  • B: shoot collected coins
